description:
Air Stunt Racing is a original, 3D high speed air racing with stunt planes!

Compete in high-adrenaline races of six, with boosters, riffles and power ups.

Main features:
-Solo or local Multiplayer (2 players)
-2 Game Modes (Arcade, Time-trial)
-6 Tracks
-8 different planes
-Full 3D
-High-Res Graphics

Show your flying skills!
name: Air Stunt Racing
